Trinity::

She walks out and makes it to the clearing. "Here we are." She looked 
around and saw bunches of animals.  Horses, birds, ground squirrels, 
hawks, badgers, lizards in the trees, huge water animals giant river 
otters, Capibara, and all sorts of other animals running about. "I'm 
sure you'll find something here that you'll like."
